  <li>Manage subscriptions, holiday pause, and quantity changes</li>
  <li>Receive delivery notifications and reminders</li>
  <li>View delivery history and payment summaries</li>
</ul>

<h3>For Local Vendors</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Onboard customers and manage subscriptions</li>
  <li>Plan and track daily delivery routes</li>
  <li>Record deliveries and reconcile payments</li>
